messages.message:
Hey team,

Does anyone know why webpacked tests would be failing on this pr (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/72924)?

```● Test suite failed to run

    fatal: master...HEAD: no merge base```
I rebased against master 5ish minutes ago, are there other known causes of this message?

It's because the branch is more than 20 commits away from master, so either:
1. the branch has > 20 commits
2. the branch is > 20 commits away from master HEAD
